  "original_title": "\u0ba4\u0bae\u0bbf\u0bb4\u0bcd \u0bae\u0bc1\u0bb1\u0bcd\u0baa\u0bcb\u0b95\u0bcd\u0b95\u0bc1 \u0b95\u0bc2\u0b9f\u0bcd\u0b9f\u0ba3\u0bbf, \u0bb8\u0bcd\u0bb0\u0bc0\u0bb2\u0b99\u0bcd\u0b95\u0bbe \u0bae\u0bc1\u0bb8\u0bcd\u0bb2\u0bbf\u0bae\u0bcd \u0b95\u0bbe\u0b99\u0bcd\u0b95\u0bbf\u0bb0\u0bb8\u0bcd, \u0b87\u0bb2\u0b99\u0bcd\u0b95\u0bc8 \u0bae\u0b95\u0bcd\u0b95\u0bb3\u0bcd \u0b95\u0bbe\u0b99\u0bcd\u0b95\u0bbf\u0bb0\u0bb8\u0bcd \u0b86\u0b95\u0bbf\u0baf\u0ba9 \u0b9f\u0bb2\u0bb8\u0bc1\u0b95\u0bcd\u0b95\u0bc1 \u0b86\u0ba4\u0bb0\u0bb5\u0bc1",
  "text_idx": {
    "en": {
      "title": "Tamil Progressive Alliance, Sri Lanka Muslim Congress and Sri Lanka People's Congress supported Dulles",
      "author": "",
      "body_lines": [
        "Tamil Progressive Alliance will support Dulles Alagaperuma, who has agreed to act as a coalition with the United People's Alliance, in the presidential polls to be held tomorrow, its president Mano Ganesan said.",
        "The decision to this effect was taken by the leadership committee of the Tamil Progressive Alliance today at the Colombo Nugegodai party secretariat under the leadership of the alliance leader Mano Ganesan.",
        "Meanwhile, Sri Lanka Muslim Congress General Secretary Nizam Kariapar has announced that the Sri Lanka Muslim Congress has decided to vote for Member of Parliament Dalus Alagaperuma in the referendum to elect the President.",
        "Also, it is noteworthy that the All Sri Lankan People's Congress has also decided to vote for Member of Parliament Dulles Alagaperuma in the referendum to elect the President."
      ],
